<section class="section-padding" aria-labelledby="ShippingHeading">
  <div class="container--narrow container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Policies</span>
    <h1 id="ShippingHeading" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>
    <p class="text-muted" style="margin-bottom:40px;max-width:560px;">The short version: we ship fast, and we stand behind every piece.</p>

    <div class="faq__list">

      <!-- Shipping -->
      <div class="faq__item">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          Where do you ship?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          <p>Canada only for now. We are based in Vancouver, BC and ship Canada-wide from our print partner's North American fulfilment centres.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          How long does shipping take?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          <p style="margin-bottom:8px;">Production takes 1–2 business days. Once it ships, Canadian orders typically arrive within 3–8 business days depending on your province. You will receive tracking by email as soon as your order leaves our print partner's facility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          Is shipping free?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          <p>Free standard shipping on orders over $95 CAD. Flat-rate shipping on everything else — the exact cost shows at checkout before you pay.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Returns -->
      <div class="faq__item" style="margin-top:24px;border-top:2px solid var(--color-border);padding-top:8px;">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          What if I do not like my portrait?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          <p>You see a full preview before you pay, so most people only order when they are happy with how it looks. If something about the printed product is not right, email us within 30 days and we will work it out. Our team is fair and will do its best to make sure you are satisfied.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          What if my order arrives damaged?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          <p>Send us a photo of the damage and we will ship a replacement at no charge. No need to return the damaged one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          Can I cancel my order?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          <p>If your order has not entered production yet, we can cancel and refund it. Just email us as soon as possible. Once production starts, we cannot cancel — but if there is an issue with your print, contact us and we will work it out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:40px;padding:24px;background:var(--color-surface);border-radius:12px;text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--color-muted);margin:0;">Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@petprintables.ca" style="color:var(--color-ink);text-decoration:underline;">hello@petprintables.ca</a> and we will get back to you within one business day.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping & Returns",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Shipping & Returns" }]
}
{% endschema %}
